@baseUrl = http://localhost:9094

### Actuator
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator
Accept: application/json

### Create a Lender
POST {{baseUrl}}/lenders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "phone": "351911195160",
  "bankData": "IBAN:PT503239218390123801",
  "address": "0 Fools Street"
}

